      "html": "<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4d748d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b4d748d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"> </p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" style=\"color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://sxma.sxtech.eu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SXMA</a></span></span><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;\">,</span></span> short for Sex Marketing Awards, returns for its second edition on 26 June 2026 in Berlin. The event brings together innovators setting new standards in storytelling, product design, community engagement, and cultural impact. SXMA serves as a meeting point for those moving the pleasure industry forward with a modern touch, creativity, and purpose.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"> </p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">The SXMA Awards honour excellence across 12 key categories, including Best Social Media Campaign, Best Creator Platform Collaboration, Best Design, Best Growth Marketing Tool, Best Community Engagement Product, and more. The awards highlight ideas and forward-thinking brands that are reshaping how pleasure, sex, and intimacy are marketed and communicated through campaigns, products, and design ideas.</span></p><p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"> </p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5209b1e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5209b1e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-830d4a6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"830d4a6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57d715b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"57d715b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt-1.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-830\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt-1.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt-1-300x300-5.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt-1-150x150-5.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c9d3f1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5c9d3f1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dadbbde elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"dadbbde\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt1.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-829\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/sxt1.webp 